title: Tens Machine for Period Pain Relief - M50 Menstrual Relax - Period Pain Relief & Endometriosis Machine - Wireless Period Pain Relief Machine with 6 Massage Modes 20 Intensity Levels for Relaxation
features: DRUG-FREE PERIOD PAIN AND ENDOMETRIOSIS RELIEF: Experience effective relief from period cramps and endometriosis pain with our Wireless TENS Machine. Using medically-researched transcutaneous electrical nerve stimulation (TENS) technology, this device offers a safe, non-invasive, and drug-free solution to alleviate discomfort.

CUSTOMISABLE PAIN RELIEF MODES: Tailor your relief to your needs with 6 massage modes and 20 intensity levels. Whether targeting cramps on your lower abdomen, back, or other muscle groups, this machine provides personalised relaxation and pain relief at the touch of a button.

RECHARGEABLE AND LONG-LASTING BATTERY LIFE: Enjoy up to 14 hours of use on a single charge. With a quick 2-hour charging time, the rechargeable battery provides up to one week of daily 40-minute sessions without needing to recharge. Perfect for reliable, on-the-go pain management.

LIGHTWEIGHT, PORTABLE, AND DISCREET: Designed for your active lifestyle, this compact device can be worn discreetly under clothing, whether you’re at home, at work, or on the move. Lightweight and easy to carry, it’s your perfect companion for uninterrupted relief throughout the day.

REUSABLE AND SKIN-FRIENDLY ADHESIVE PADS: Our TENS machine comes with high-quality, irritant-free adhesive pads that can be reused up to 30 times. Replacement pads are easily and affordably available, ensuring you always have reliable support when needed.

VERSATILE PAIN RELIEF FOR MULTIPLE CONDITIONS: More than just period pain relief—this device is also ideal for relieving arthritis, sciatica, labour pain, and muscle tension in the legs, neck, or back. With clinically proven Programmes for pain relief and muscle stimulation, it’s a must-have for comprehensive care.

product_details_tab_data.Safety Warning: Always read the instructions before use. Keep out of reach of children. Do not use if you have a pacemaker or other electronic medical device. Consult your doctor before use if you are pregnant, have epilepsy, or any other medical condition. Do not use on broken or irritated skin. Avoid contact with eyes and mouth. Store in a cool, dry place. Do not expose to excessive heat or moisture. Unplug the device when not in use. In case of accidental ingestion, seek medical advice immediately. In case of fire, use a suitable extinguisher. Do not use the device if the cord is damaged or if it makes a sudden noise or produces an unusual smell. If you experience any discomfort or adverse effects, discontinue use and consult your doctor.
